	(text_box "Note!  Original board can have 2364 masked ROMs (24-pin), 2764 EPROMs (28-pins), or both.\nThere are three jumper blocks (J1/J2/J3) that configure each ROM socket.\nFor simplicity they are all represented as 2764 here.\n\nExample:\nU2 ... D32522E/MONITOR3 (2364)\nU3 ... D32521E (2764)\nU4 ... D32351E/BIT-99C1 (2364)"
